Module ci553.ministore

module ci553.ministore
Module definition for the CI553 MiniStore application. This module requires various JavaFX modules, Java SQL, and Java RMI. It also requires Apache Derby modules for database operations. The module opens specific packages for JavaFX FXML and exports packages for use by other modules.
